    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Operations on arrays"
      ],
      "id": "f4c15fcf"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.arange(9).reshape(3, 3)\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "255dbf22",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.transpose(data)"
      ],
      "id": "2252e8c4",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---"
      ],
      "id": "24d24ab4"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.random.randn(1, 2, 3, 4, 5)"
      ],
      "id": "49ba2c07",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data.shape"
      ],
      "id": "e326a8eb",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data.T.shape"
      ],
      "id": "f800fe3c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Matrix and vector operations"
      ],
      "id": "dbb859d7"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.arange(1, 7).reshape(2, 3)\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "0f3d6a38",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B = np.arange(1, 7).reshape(3, 2)\n",
        "B"
      ],
      "id": "a84bc68b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.dot(A, B)"
      ],
      "id": "afadc081",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.dot(B, A)"
      ],
      "id": "887fc838",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A @ B  # python 3.5 above"
      ],
      "id": "bc776752",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B @ A"
      ],
      "id": "74e8c3da",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---"
      ],
      "id": "46b3634f"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.arange(9).reshape(3, 3)\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "e4afe41a",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x = np.arange(3)\n",
        "x"
      ],
      "id": "8c6f5241",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.dot(A, x)"
      ],
      "id": "bc8eea9e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A.dot(x)"
      ],
      "id": "72adbcc9",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A @ x"
      ],
      "id": "0513cc0b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---"
      ],
      "id": "afc86413"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.random.rand(3, 3)\n",
        "B = np.random.rand(3, 3)"
      ],
      "id": "9473e1be",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Ap = np.dot(B, np.dot(A, np.linalg.inv(B)))"
      ],
      "id": "e7cb21f6",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Ap = B.dot(A.dot(np.linalg.inv(B)))"
      ],
      "id": "f74fcd14",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B @ A @ np.linalg.inv(B)"
      ],
      "id": "d459fa1a",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---"
      ],
      "id": "f4b46a24"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.inner(x, x)"
      ],
      "id": "55456768",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.dot(x, x)"
      ],
      "id": "5bd6a7c7",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "y = x[:, np.newaxis]\n",
        "y"
      ],
      "id": "d52fc2f6",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.dot(y.T, y)"
      ],
      "id": "771338d9",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n",
        "\n",
        "* Given two vectors, $\\mathbf{a} = [a_0, a_1, ..., a_M]~$ and $~\\mathbf{b} = [b_0, b_1, ..., b_N]$, $~$the outer product is $\\mathbf{a}^T\\mathbf{b}$\n",
        "\n",
        "$$\\begin{pmatrix}\n",
        " a_0 b_0 & a_0b_1 & \\cdots & a_0 b_N \\\\\n",
        " a_1 b_0 & \\cdots & \\cdots & a_1 b_N \\\\\n",
        " \\vdots  & \\ddots &        & \\vdots  \\\\\n",
        " a_M b_0 &        & \\ddots & a_M b_N \\\\\n",
        " \\end{pmatrix}\n",
        "$$\n"
      ],
      "id": "c5a7f952"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x = np.array([1, 2, 3])"
      ],
      "id": "90bcaf14",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.outer(x, x)"
      ],
      "id": "99849a4e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.kron(x, x)"
      ],
      "id": "63d988b3",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.kron(x[:, np.newaxis], x[np.newaxis, :])"
      ],
      "id": "63c624af",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.kron(np.ones((2, 2)), np.identity(2))"
      ],
      "id": "e4408738",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.kron(np.identity(2), np.ones((2, 2)))"
      ],
      "id": "514b106c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---"
      ],
      "id": "a6d63552"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x = np.array([1, 2, 3, 4])\n",
        "y = np.array([5, 6, 7, 8])"
      ],
      "id": "4b3191c5",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.einsum(\"n,n\", x, y)"
      ],
      "id": "6d5a85a3",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.inner(x, y)"
      ],
      "id": "b9308a1f",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.arange(9).reshape(3, 3)\n",
        "B = A.T"
      ],
      "id": "ad17c3c6",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.einsum(\"mk,kn\", A, B)"
      ],
      "id": "fa0bc120",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.alltrue(np.einsum(\"mk,kn\", A, B) == np.dot(A, B))"
      ],
      "id": "95f5b6c5",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    }
